## Third-Party Data Sources

This project utilizes public data from the following sources.
Please refer to each source's terms of use:

- **NEIS 교육정보 개방 포털** (https://open.neis.go.kr)
  - Ministry of Education, 17 Metropolitan Education Offices
  - Data: 학교기본정보, 급식식단정보

- **학교알리미** (https://open.schoolinfo.go.kr)
  - KERIS (Korea Education and Research Information Service)
  - Data: 학교정보공시

- **공공데이터포털** (https://www.data.go.kr)
  - Public data provided by Government 3.0

## Third-Party Libraries

- **Leaflet.js** (BSD-2-Clause) - https://leafletjs.com
- **Chart.js** (MIT) - https://www.chartjs.org
- **Pretendard Font** (SIL OFL) - https://github.com/orioncactus/pretendard
- **JetBrains Mono** (Apache 2.0) - https://www.jetbrains.com/lp/mono/
- **Anthropic Claude API** - https://www.anthropic.com (Commercial Service)

